import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Helmet } from 'react-helmet';
import GeneralBanner from '../Common/BannerParts/GeneralBanner';

class BasementRenovationsInVaughan extends Component {
  static propTypes = {
  };

  state = {
  };

  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Helmet>
          <title>AGM Basements | Basement Renovations in Vaughan</title>
        </Helmet>
        <GeneralBanner title="Basement Renovations in Vaughan" />
        <div className="container">
          <p>With a portfolio of over 150 basements in the area of Vaughan, AGM Basements is proud to offer an experienced and creative service. Renowned as specialists in the field, our basements are all shapes and sizes and offer affordable desirable solutions to implement your vision for your basement.</p>
          <h3>We tackle any basement renovation in Vaughan</h3>
          <p>AGM has a dedicated group of basement contractors who work in perfect harmony with clients to ensure complete satisfaction and transparency throughout the basement renovation experience. As no two basements are the same, we have experience in all kinds of homes, regardless of age, size, or location.</p>
          <p>Basement finishing companies don’t have an easy job when it comes to basement remodelling in Vaughan. AGM have excelled in the field for the last 18 years and our experienced team of builders, interior designers, electricians, and basement contractors are proud to offer unparalleled service in the region. We feel our high standard of satisfaction and quality speaks for itself, and much of our business is based on recommendations. </p>
          <p>We take great pride in the work we do and with no job too big or too small for our time, our dedicated team of basement builders works tirelessly to ensure that after the renovation, your basement will be your new favourite room. </p>
          <p>Some of the things we have assisted with creating in the past include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Wine cellars</li>
            <li>Kitchens</li>
            <li>Fireplaces </li>
            <li>Saunas</li>
            <li>Bars</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We’re so confident in our ability to complete your basement remodelling that we welcome potential clients to visit one of our many finishing showcases and open houses for you to see our transformative skills. When choosing AGM, you’re choosing a company you know you can trust - we let our finished work speak for itself.</p>
          <h3>Benefits of basement renovations</h3>
          <p>There are plenty of benefits to basement renovations, including adding value to your home, bringing in additional rental income, avoiding zoning codes, and creating additional living space/guest room. Plus, AGM are more affordable compared to other home renovations and other basement renovation companies.</p>
          <h3>Looking after your home</h3>
          <p>The number one priority of all our jobs is safety and satisfaction. All of our products and basement finishes adhere to high safety standards, such as our total seal for radon, our total seal for mould and rust, and our signature water seal. Not only will your basement stay looking good for years to come, it’ll stay safe as well. </p>
          <p>With a customer guarantee as secure as our signature water seal, you can be assured we only use qualified, masterful, and dedicated tradesmen and you don’t pay a penny until the finished article is to your satisfaction. We’re so confident we even guarantee completion on time or we pay you! Please give us a call today for our free estimate service and to discover how AGM can transform your home.</p>
        </div>
      </>
    );
  }
}

export default BasementRenovationsInVaughan;
